Lais Ribeiro (born in Teresina, Piauí, 1992) is a Brazilian model. In 2009, she started modelling locally and shortly after walked the major international catwalks for such designers as Chanel, Louis Vuitton, Gucci, Dolce & Gabbana, Versace, and Marc Jacobs.
